ets/steam/apps/1158940/extras/b489edb5bb149d5504a3f980443bc9f2.poster.avif?t=1744285471\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1158940/extras/b489edb5bb149d5504a3f980443bc9f2.webm?t=1744285471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1158940/extras/b489edb5bb149d5504a3f980443bc9f2.mp4?t=1744285471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build-A-Buccaneer</h2><br>No two ships or pirates are the same! Show off your booty with a swath of customisable parts, clothing and accessories - embroidered jackets, gilded hulls, golden peg legs - you’ll get real fancy, real fast!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1158940/extras/8aadf1b257fb1546ebc8e859e19a962f.poster.avif?t=1744285471\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1158940/extras/8aadf1b257fb1546ebc8e859e19a962f.webm?t=1744285471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1158940/extras/8aadf1b257fb1546ebc8e859e19a962f.mp4?t=1744285471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
